name: 6 Queens - Queen Barika
description:
Doted on by all. Adored by many.
A flame of citrine on a mysterious night.
Her aura calms the souls of the uneasy and restless.
Her compassion for her brothers and sisters is an endless light to all those around.
She is peace.
She is solace.
In her sight you are no longer lost.
Her embrace will leave you found.
